---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="Privacy Policy - Manny Ledoux"
	description="Privacy policy for Manny Ledoux's portfolio and iOS applications"
>
	<div class="min-h-screen py-16">
		<main class="wrapper max-w-4xl mx-auto">
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

			<div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
				<p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">Last Updated: January 13, 2025</p>

				<div class="space-y-8">
					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Privacy Commitment</h2>
						<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
							I believe in respecting your privacy. This policy applies to my portfolio website (aledoux.net) 
							and all iOS applications I develop. I'm committed to protecting your personal information and 
							being transparent about any data practices.
						</p>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Information Not Collected</h2>
						<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
							I do not collect, store, or process any personal information through this website or my iOS apps unless explicitly stated. 
							This includes:
						</p>
						<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 ml-4">
							<li>No tracking cookies</li>
							<li>No analytics without consent</li>
							<li>No personal data collection</li>
							<li>No third-party tracking</li>
						</ul>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">iOS App Permissions</h2>
						<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
							If any of my iOS apps request permissions (such as camera, location, or notifications), 
							they will only be used for the app's core functionality and will be clearly explained 
							when requested. No data from these permissions is transmitted to external servers unless 
							explicitly stated in the app.
						</p>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Data Storage</h2>
						<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
							Any data created within my apps is stored locally on your device. You have full control 
							over this data and can delete it at any time by removing the app.
						</p>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
						<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
							This website is hosted on a static hosting service. Some apps may use Apple's services 
							(like iCloud sync) if you choose to enable them. Please refer to Apple's privacy policy 
							for information about their data practices.
						</p>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Children's Privacy</h2>
						<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
							My apps and website are not directed at children under 13. I do not knowingly collect 
							personal information from children.
						</p>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
						<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
							You have the right to:
						</p>
						<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 ml-4">
							<li>Know what data is being collected (none, unless stated)</li>
							<li>Access any data stored locally in apps</li>
							<li>Delete any app and its associated data</li>
							<li>Contact me with privacy concerns</li>
						</ul>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Policy Changes</h2>
						<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
							I may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this 
							page with an updated revision date.
						</p>
					</section>

					<section>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Contact</h2>
						<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
							If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please feel free to 
							contact me through GitHub or the contact form on this website.
						</p>
					</section>

					<div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-800">
						<p class="text-gray-400 text-sm italic">
							This privacy policy is designed with your privacy at its core, inspired by privacy-first 
							principles and transparent communication.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

